   "source": [
    "# FundLens Pipeline v2.0 — AMFI Direct\n",
    "\n",
    "**Data source:** AMFI (amfiindia.com) — replacing MFAPI.in entirely.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Cells\n",
    "- **Cell 0** — Setup: install deps, clone pipeline files\n",
    "- **Cell 1** — Fetch AMFI + compute returns/ratios → `fundlens_schemes.json`\n",
    "- **Cell 2** — Upload to main Gist\n",
    "- **Cell 3** — Historical backfill (run once daily — extends archive 3 months)\n",
    "- **Cell T** — Test run on 10 schemes (use before full run)\n",
    "\n",
    "## Normal daily workflow\n",
    "For daily use, the **GitHub Action runs automatically at 10pm IST** — you don't need to open Colab at all.\n",
    "Use Colab for: development, debugging, manual re-runs if GitHub Action fails.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# ─── Cell 0: Setup ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "# Run once per Colab session to install dependencies and load pipeline files.\n",
    "\n",
    "!pip install requests python-dateutil -q\n",
    "\n",
    "import os, sys\n",
    "\n",
    "# If running from Colab (not local), download pipeline files from your GitHub repo\n",
    "GITHUB_REPO = 'anjaneyakg/fundlens'   # your repo\n",
    "BRANCH      = 'main'\n",
    "PIPELINE_FILES = [\n",
    "    'pipeline/amfi_normalise.py',\n",
    "    'pipeline/validate.py',\n",
    "    'pipeline/pipeline_cell1.py',\n",
    "    'pipeline/pipeline_cell2.py',\n",
    "    'pipeline/pipeline_cell3_backfill.py',\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "os.makedirs('pipeline', exist_ok=True)\n",
    "for filepath in PIPELINE_FILES:\n",
    "    filename = filepath.split('/')[-1]\n",
    "    url = f'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/{GITHUB_REPO}/{BRANCH}/{filepath}'\n",
    "    !wget -q -O pipeline/{filename} {url}\n",
    "    print(f'  Downloaded: {filename}')\n",
    "\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, 'pipeline')\n",
    "print('\\n✅ Setup complete. Ready to run Cell 1.')"
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": []
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
